{"tid":1134813,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港產前中情局人員認串謀間諜 向華洩露美國機密資料","createTime":"2019-05-02T02:20:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T06:29:52.000Z","uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a035e5b9467848ab3220bb4a3268d6c38f1e8fd0","tid":1134813,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T02:20:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B8%AF%E7%94%A2%E5%89%8D%E4%B8%AD%E6%83%85%E5%B1%80%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E8%AA%8D%E4%B8%B2%E8%AC%80%E9%96%93%E8%AB%9C-%E5%90%91%E8%8F%AF%E6%B4%A9%E9%9C%B2%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%A9%9F%E5%AF%86%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99-225800503.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%2594%25A2%25E5%2589%258D%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%2583%2585%25E5%25B1%2580%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25AA%258D%25E4%25B8%25B2%25E8%25AC%2580%25E9%2596%2593%25E8%25AB%259C-%25E5%2590%2591%25E8%258F%25AF%25E6%25B4%25A9%25E9%259C%25B2%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%25AF%2586%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%2596%2599-225800503.html&d=P2v3VPQ3iBAPr6cjv61qmUPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=1dc16c94\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B8%AF%E7%94%A2%E5%89%8D%E4%B8%AD%E6%83%85%E5%B1%80%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E8%AA%8D%E4%B8%B2%E8%AC%80%E9%96%93%E8%AB%9C-%E5%90%91%E8%8F%AF%E6%B4%A9%E9%9C%B2%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%A9%9F%E5%AF%86%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99-225800503.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/PvpJMlrGyKFiTwDTTCcuVA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20190502a070154.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FPvpJMlrGyKFiTwDTTCcuVA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20190502a070154.jpg&h=a5d18f5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李振成承認罪串謀進行間諜活動。網上圖片<br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】擁有香港永久居留權的前美國中情局（CIA）情報人員李振成（Jerry Chun Shing Lee），去年1月被美國指控為中國當間諜後一直還押，同年5月被控三項間諜罪名，指李振成向中國政府透露危害美國的國防資料，最高可被判終身監禁。李振成承認罪串謀進行間諜活動，將美國國防機密資料交予中國政府的罪名。<br />\n<br />\n根據法庭文件紀錄，李振成將於周三在維珍尼亞州亞歷山德里亞聯邦法院，出席更改答辯聆訊（change-of-plea hearing）。法庭文件紀錄沒有顯示他將會承認哪一條控罪，亦不清楚他是否會請求較輕的指控或較輕的判決，而李的代表律師回覆媒體時，表示不予置評。<br />\n<br />\n起訴書披露，李振成由2010年起接觸中國情報官員，對方更即時給他10萬美元現金及提出「照顧他一生」（they would take care of him for life）來換取合作，中間人是曾任香港警察、李的生意拍檔。約兩周後，李振成主動向一名CIA前同事匯報，曾有中方人員接觸，但並無提及金錢回報及照顧他一生之說。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd3419d3c12bf36a832eb7b369daa06c6656d62e","tid":1134813,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T02:23:00.000Z","msg":"靚仔過共諜大灣駒, 咁就比人捉左, 地球上又少一個靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2382773bdeb5370ca49a56b64db7a98511c3df6e","tid":1134813,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T02:24:30.000Z","msg":"前任警察做共諜"},{"pid":"8010db5399fd608d9e395922898d430ded33ab8e","tid":1134813,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T06:29:52.000Z","msg":"李振成由2010年起接觸中國情報官員，對方更即時給他10萬美元現金及提出「照顧他一生」（they would take care of him for life）來換取合作，中間人是曾任香港警察、李的生意拍檔。<br />\n<br />\n曾任警察係邊個呀？"}]}